Class LabelPropagation

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.graphreduction.communitydetection.CommunityDetectionImpl
      • main.java.graphreduction.communitydetection.LabelPropagation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommunityDetection
    public class LabelPropagation
extends CommunityDetectionImpl
    The LabelPropagation Class extends the CommunityDetectionImpl. The Label Propagation algorithm (LPA) is a fast algorithm for finding communities in a graph. LPA works by propagating labels throughout the network and forming communities based on this process of label propagation.

    Also see: Neo4j docs

    Version:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Catherine Camier
